des:
I have 5 answers about my professional aspirations and background. You can ask 1 of the 5 questions listed below.

- What do you love about ux design?
- What are you looking for in a ux design position?
- What do you think are the top priorities of conversational design?
- Which apps do you consider to have good ux?
- What are three words to describe yourself?

Email me at joannasiu12@gmail.com if you would like me to join your team!
Note: you must ask the questions with the exact wording providing.
